<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <style>
        .page-hero {
            background: #1a1a1a;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 80px 40px;
        }
        .page-hero h1 { font-size: 42px; font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .page-hero p { color: #aaa; font-size: 14px; }
        .about-content {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 80px auto;
            padding: 0 40px;
            line-height: 1.9;
            color: #444;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .about-content h2 { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #1a1a1a; }
        .back-link { display: inline-block; margin-top: 40px; color: #1a1a1a; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; }
        .back-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="container-nav">
            <div class="menu-btn">☰ Menu</div>
            <div class="logo">
                <a href="/">
                    <img src="https://uniworthshop.com/cdn/shop/files/LogoSVG_bbf8eed2-7cfd-4bb6-9d51-cac4d718fe55_450x.svg?v=1761913704" alt="Uniworth Logo">
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="nav-icons">
                <span class="icon">🔍</span>
                <span class="icon">👤</span>
                <span class="icon cart-icon">🛒 <span class="cart-badge">0</span></span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="page-hero">
        <h1>About Uniworth</h1>
        <p>Pakistan's No. 1 Shirt Brand</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-content">
        <h2>Our Story</h2>
        <p>
            Uniworth is a menswear brand, designed entirely in-house, standing alone as Pakistan's
            No. 1 Shirt Brand. From timeless tailoring to premium formal shirts, we present a
            considered edit of quality, wearable clothes, and accessories bearing the Uniworth name.
        </p>
        <p>
            Our collections are built around the modern Pakistani man — confident, refined, and
            rooted in culture while embracing contemporary style. Every stitch, every fabric, every
            detail is chosen with intention.
        </p>
        <h2>Our Commitment</h2>
        <p>
            We believe in craftsmanship that lasts. Our garments are made from premium fabrics
            sourced with care, ensuring comfort and durability season after season.
        </p>
        <a href="/" class="back-link">← Back to Home</a>
    </div>

    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="copyright">
            <p>UNIWORTH DRESS CO. All Rights Reserved. | Privacy Policy</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
